{"an10.213:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 10.213 ","an10.213:0.2":"21. Karajakayavagga ","an10.213:0.3":"Matugamasutta ","an10.213:1.1":"“Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannagato matugamo yathabhatam nikkhitto evam niraye. ","an10.213:1.2":"Katamehi dasahi? ","an10.213:1.3":"Panatipati hoti …pe… ","an10.213:1.4":"adinnadayi hoti … ","an10.213:1.5":"kamesumicchacari hoti … ","an10.213:1.6":"musavadi hoti … ","an10.213:1.7":"pisunavaco hoti … ","an10.213:1.8":"pharusavaco hoti … ","an10.213:1.9":"samphappalapi hoti … ","an10.213:1.10":"abhijjhalu hoti … ","an10.213:1.11":"byapannacitto hoti … ","an10.213:1.12":"micchaditthiko hoti …. ","an10.213:1.13":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannagato matugamo yathabhatam nikkhitto evam niraye. ","an10.213:2.1":"Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannagato matugamo yathabhatam nikkhitto evam sagge. ","an10.213:2.2":"Katamehi dasahi? ","an10.213:2.3":"Panatipata pativirato hoti …pe… ","an10.213:2.4":"adinnadana pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.5":"kamesumicchacara pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.6":"musavada pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.7":"pisunaya vacaya pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.8":"pharusaya vacaya pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.9":"samphappalapa pativirato hoti … ","an10.213:2.10":"anabhijjhalu hoti … ","an10.213:2.11":"abyapannacitto hoti … ","an10.213:2.12":"sammaditthiko hoti …. ","an10.213:2.13":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannagato matugamo yathabhatam nikkhitto evam sagge”ti. ","an10.213:2.14":"Tatiyam. "}